### Description
SounDex is a cross-blockchain DeFi vApp that connects traders with the best prices,
protects liquidity providers from the risk of impermanent loss,
and automatically optimizes liquidity. One app, all DeFi solutions.

### SL Integration  
use Soundness Layer to $SNDX Token → governance token for voting, staking, and revenue-sharing.

